Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:40.06,5-normal,signs,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fs100\bord0\shad0\pos(960,324)}Menembus Waktu Pasir
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.37,0:00:15.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.12,0:00:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.92,0:00:21.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma sedikit gugup.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya, tahu sendiri tujuan kita, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi kali ini Ram dan Rem juga ikut.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada Meili juga yang menemani,\Nserta Anastasia yang jadi pemandu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.43,0:00:36.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu,\Naku juga harus melindungimu, Subaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.18,0:00:37.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga dihitung sebagai orang\Nyang dilindungi?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.47,0:00:42.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.98,0:00:47.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya mereka tidak suka\Nbau binatang iblis di tubuhku.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Joseph!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.03,0:00:50.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lepaskan dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.74,0:00:53.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.03,0:00:59.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan mengelus lehernya seperti ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.62,0:01:02.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,biasanya naga darat akan tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.63,0:01:05.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa benar begitu, Patrasche?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kayaknya dia susah, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.80,0:01:13.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Abang, tolong jangan biarkan aku\Nsendirian dengannya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.97,0:01:16.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takutnya nanti aku dimakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.31,0:01:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal ngeri begitu mana mungkin terjadi!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Patrasche itu vegetarian.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru, Nona Emilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengenai tubuh Ram...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.15,0:01:28.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.33,0:01:34.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk lebih jelasnya,\Ntanyakan langsung pada Ram dan Beatrice.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.66,0:01:35.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan melakukan yang terbaik demi Ram.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persiapan untuk mereka berdua sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ram, berhati-hatilah dalam perjalanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.01,0:01:54.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah mengabulkan\Npermintaan egoisku.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.47,0:01:58.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami pasti akan pulang membawa\Nhasil yang Tuan Roswaal harapkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan... Subaru, hati-hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Petra dan Frederica,\Naku titip rumah selama kami pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.80,0:02:08.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, waktunya ke Gurun Pasir Augria!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berangkat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pesan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Susu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang dingin.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Susu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang hangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama sekali tidak kelihatan\Nsedang ramai, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kayaknya waktu pasir memang bikin sepi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, ini kota yang jarang\Ndidatangi orang luar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.63,0:04:38.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa yang kalian lakukan di Mirula\Nsaat waktu pasir begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.01,0:04:41.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Singkatnya, menaklukkan Gurun Augria.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bermaksud jahat,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi pulanglah sebelum mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.52,0:04:52.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti ada, 'kan?\NSituasi di mana tidak bisa mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Empat ratus tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada seorang pun\Nyang pernah mencapai menara itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.74,0:05:06.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di gurun itu ada binatang iblis\Ndan miasma penyihir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.74,0:05:10.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian takkan bisa mendekati menara\Nyang terlihat dari kejauhan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa pulang hidup itu sudah untung,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,kebanyakan orang berakhir\Nterkubur di dalam pasir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bermaksud jahat,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,jangan lakukan hal bodoh...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.13,0:05:25.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman benar-benar mengkhawatirkan kami, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya saja, banyak anak-anak muda
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.07,0:05:34.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,seperti kalian yang selalu muncul\Nberulang kali.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih minumannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih juga sudah berbagi cerita.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ceritamu sungguh membantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.24,0:05:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini cerita sekitar setahun belakangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.38,0:06:00.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Banyak yang melihat burung terbang\Nke arah gurun.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kata mereka yang melihatnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.34,0:06:07.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,burung-burung itu tampak terbang\Nmenuju ke arah menara.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, carilah burung itu\Nkalau kalian tersesat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika beruntung,\Nmungkin mereka bisa menuntun kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.94,0:06:16.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, kalau sampai mengandalkan itu di gurun,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,berarti kalian sedang sial banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menara Pengawas Pleiades.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menara sang Bijak yang penuh misteri, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana roh-rohmu sejak kau dilupakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada perubahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.21,0:06:45.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka masih ada di sisiku,\Nhanya saja tampak kebingungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya Berkah Pengundang Roh\Nmilikku masih ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alasan mereka enggan menjauh dariku...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya belum ada jawabannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.14,0:06:58.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun dilupakan,\Nbukan berarti kontraknya ikut hilang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,kini aku hanya bisa melakukan\Ntugas kesatria dengan pedangku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan tidak bisa menggunakan sihir roh,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,artinya kekuatanku telah menurun drastis.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa malah wajahmu\Nyang terlihat lebih kesal?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.96,0:07:16.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sembarangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Informasi dari mana aku kesal\Ngara-gara kau jadi lemah?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.26,0:07:29.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka, kau tidak pandai\Nmenyembunyikan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena belakangan ini\Nkita bepergian bersama?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa aku mulai bisa membacamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pun sama,\Nkalau ke depannya tidak terjadi apa-apa,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisa-bisa saat sampai di menara,\Naku bakal jadi Ahli Julius.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena sekarang pun, tanpa diragukan lagi,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau adalah orang yang paling mengenalku\Ndi dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malah dapat gelar\Nyang paling tidak aku inginkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.16,0:07:58.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru, sekarang bukan waktunya\Nmain-main, kurasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya waktu pasir akan segera dimulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berjuanglah, Patrasche! Joseph juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Angin dan miasma.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati juga dengan binatang iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.23,0:08:29.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, jangan sampai kehilangan\Njejak menara dan tersesat, kurasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dibilang tersesat pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukankah lebih sulit melewatkan\Nbenda besar itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beti juga setuju.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tidak aneh kalau sesuatu terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Faktanya, belum pernah ada seorang pun\Nyang berhasil mencapainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anastasia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini betulan tidak apa-apa kita lurus terus?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, Natsuki, kau curigaan banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ini satu nasib.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percayalah padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.48,0:09:06.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir percaya pada rubah itu\Nmudah dilakukan, kurasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh? Kau cerita padanya, Natsuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anastasia harusnya tidak keberatan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan tepati janjiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa kau sedang bekerja, Meili?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.21,0:09:30.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak masuk gurun, kita belum pernah\Nketemu binatang iblis, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi itu gara-gara kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.14,0:09:39.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nakan kutunjukkan betapa pentingnya aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cacing pasir.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.04,0:10:05.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak pernah dengar\Nada yang sebesar itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penilaianmu terhadapku sudah berubah?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin cepat-cepat keluar\Ndari gurun ini dan mandi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setuju.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.92,0:10:57.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi harusnya kalian sudah\Nmenyadarinya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kita terus lurus...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jarak ke menara tidak berkurang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.14,0:11:09.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ini maksudnya Reinhard\Ntidak berhasil sampai ke sana?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruang di sekitar kita terpelintir.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruangnya terpelintir?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.65,0:11:18.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,menara dan gurun ini tersambung,\Ntapi sebenarnya tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.57,0:11:24.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa jadi kita hanya berputar-putar\Ndi tempat yang sama terus.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi ini alasan Gurun Augria\Ndisebut tempat berbahaya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus, kita juga mau menyerah\Noleh ruang terpelintir
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang menelan banyak petualang ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.80,0:11:40.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sinilah peranku menjadi pemandu\Nmenuju Menara Pengawas Pleiades.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau pedagang sudah turun tangan,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,artinya kita datang untuk menang, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.31,0:11:50.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu artinya, Nona Anastasia bisa melihat\Njalan menuju menara?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Angin kencang saat "waktu pasir"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah reaksi saat ruang yang terpelintir\Nkembali semula.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.74,0:11:59.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya, ketika waktu pasir berlangsung,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,ruang yang terpelintir memiliki\Nretakan yang terbuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.74,0:12:06.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di retakan terbuka tersebut\Nterdapat lautan pasir yang sesungguhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lautan pasir yang sesungguhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, orang yang memiliki peran penting
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk menemukan retakan tersebut adalah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.23,0:12:31.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penglihatan jauh Ram,\Ndengan meminjam kekuatan binatang iblis.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bicara soal binatang iblis\Nyang aktif di waktu pasir,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,harusnya ada yang berpapasan\Ndengan ruang yang terpelintir.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.24,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Sedikit ke utara.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cacing pasir kali, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:41.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meili harus mencari lokasi binatang iblis
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan memberitahukannya pada Ram.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sambungannya terputus.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.07,0:12:59.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru, kita tak bisa membebani Ram\Nlebih dari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.13,0:12:59.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Emilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada orang lain yang bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Peran ini hanya bisa dilakukan olehku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.64,0:13:10.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meili, abaikan saja binatang iblis\Ndi dalam pasir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada gunanya kalau yang terlihat\Ncuma pasir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa membedakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harusnya kau jangan langsung menyerah dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya cara kita tidak salah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.37,0:13:26.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggal masalah takdir saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.62,0:13:30.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bicara keberuntungan,\Nkita ini payah banget, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Burung!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisanya terbang di langit yang begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Burung?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru, burung...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ram, bisa kau sambungkan penglihatanmu\Ndengan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Burung itu adalah kuncinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.62,0:14:06.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dapat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini kita pasti bisa lewati waktu pasir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lurus.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lurus terus.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka sudah tidak bisa\Nmenanggung beban lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.67,0:14:57.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhasil! Bisa tembus!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya! Berhasil!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.09,0:15:02.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dekat telinga berisik banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa pasang muka lempeng begitu?\NHarusnya ikut senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, hore!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore, kurasa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukti kalau panggung sudah berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.77,0:15:18.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gurun pasir berubah jadi hamparan bunga...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hamparan... bunga?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beruang oiran.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru, ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penglihatan Ram terputus...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setop.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Emilia, diam dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan berisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bergerak.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.95,0:16:11.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Celaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia datang! Dia datang! Dia datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasakan! Terima semua ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang hebat, Emilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusu, kalau tak ingin mati,\Nlarilah sekuat tenaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lah, Ram?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.41,0:16:54.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa biarkan Nona Emilia\Nmenanggung beban sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial, aku tak boleh kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beako, kau sanggup?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.00,0:17:02.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru kau sendiri yang jangan\Nkehabisan tenaga dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minya!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, cacing pasir!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hancurkan mereka semua!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggal sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus maju sampai ke menara pengawas.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati? Hidup lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok bisa? Kapan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.29,0:17:39.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?\NKenapa bisa mati?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat! Gawat! Gawat! Gawat...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Celaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.97,0:17:48.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juli...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.05,0:17:52.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lari! Lari! Lari! Lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasakan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beatrice.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minya!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.32,0:18:10.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, cacing pasir jagoanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serang!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begini polanya bakal sama lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.37,0:18:24.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusu, kalau tak ingin mati,\Nlarilah sekuat tenaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ram, jangan langsung lurus ke menara!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.84,0:18:27.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ubah arah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bicara apa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tinggal lurus.\NJalan lain penuh binatang iblis!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru jangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pokoknya kita ubah arah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ram, turuti saja apa kata Subaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak mungkin Subaru tiba-tiba\Nbicara aneh tanpa dipikir dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.56,0:18:45.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setiap hari Barusu suka bicara\Nomong kosong dan tak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di saat berbahaya begini,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak mungkin Subaru tiba-tiba\Nbicara aneh tanpa dipikir dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah repot-repot dikoreksi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian yang di atas!\NJangan sampai jatuh!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Awas!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hampir saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru, gawat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kita terpisah dari kereta Emilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang hanya kita sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.86,0:19:41.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lawan si bedebah Regulus\Nmasih lebih gampang daripada ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada waktu untuk mengeluh.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus cari Emilia dan lain...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang berpikir!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada sesuatu...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.03,0:20:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Subaru! Subaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, jangan mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan buat Beti sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan tinggalkan Beti sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suba...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penyebab matiku yang pertama dan kedua...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beako, aku mencintaimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tangan Tak Terlihat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin tanya satu hal pada kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang lihat cahaya bersinar sekejap\Ndari menara?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cahaya dari menara?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.82,0:21:47.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutmu, cahaya itu bagaimana, Barusu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.67,0:21:51.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku... itu sesuatu yang berbahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya bukan sesuatu yang ramah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berdasarkan insting?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, bahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, cuma insting, lo?\NKau percaya?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Insting Subaru, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa sebaiknya kita waspada.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.17,0:22:10.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ram?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.90,0:22:13.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusu...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.06,0:22:15.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia melihatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.44,0:22:21.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan kubiarkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.55,0:22:40.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jarum?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusu, ada yang datang lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.47,0:22:43.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beako, kau bisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertanyaan bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,EMT!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.61,0:22:58.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihir pembatalan mutlak. EMT.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.83,0:23:05.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam area ini, sihir tidak akan berfungsi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.07,0:23:08.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya saja, ini tak bisa bertahan lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.87,0:23:09.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.37,0:23:14.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruang yang terpelintir ini rusak\Ngara-gara EMT!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.71,0:23:15.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.75,0:23:18.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu pasir punya konsep yang sama\Nseperti Pintu Perlintasan Beako!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.47,0:23:38.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketemu.
